      <title>食肉动物的剑齿进化了很多次。这是否导致了它们的灭绝？</title>
      <link>https://www.npr.org/2025/01/21/g-s1-43731/saber-teeth-in-predators-evolved-many-times-did-it-lead-to-their-extinction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新分析表明，剑齿虎的牙齿高度擅长刺穿猎物，但最终却以牺牲耐用性为代价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.npr.org/2025/01/21/g-s1-43731/saber-teeth-in-predators-evolved-many-times-did-it-lead-to-their-extinction</guid>
